message: The 'growth serum' tool is reusable and consistently increases item value, even for negative items, up to a certain point. Use it on all base ingredients. Combining 2-3 'grown' items typically creates a valuable hybrid. Be cautious combining 4 or more items; this often results in an 'overcomplicated' item with a severe negative value.
